Class Command

java.lang.Object
  Command
All Implemented Interfaces:
Serializable
public class Command
extends Object
implements Serializable

This class holds information about a command issued by the user. Each command has two parts: a CommandWord and a list of parameters If the command had only one word, then the parameter list is empty.

Version:
01.11.10
